==English==
{{wikipedia|Malagasy language}}
===Proper noun===
'''Malagasy'''

# A person from [[Madagascar]] or of Malagasy descent.
# A language spoken in [[Madagascar]].

====Translations====

*Chinese: [[马尔加什人]] (mǎrjiāshí-rén)
*French: [[Malgache]] {{mf}} (1), [[malgache]] {{m}} (2)
*German: [[Madagasse]] {{m}}, [[Madagassin]] {{f}}
*Gujarati: [[માલાગાસી]] {{f}} (1) {{mf}} (2)
*Hindi: [[मालागासी]] {{f}} (1) {{mf}} (2)

===Adjective===
'''Malagasy'''

# Of, from, or pertaining to Madagascar, the Malagasy people or the Malagasy language.

====Translations====
*Chinese: [[马尔加什的]] (mǎrjiāshí de)
*French: [[malgache]]
*German: [[madagassisch]]
*Gujarati: [[માલાગાસી]]
*Hindi: [[मालागासी]]

